{!<div id="young-plan-chart"></div>!}

@young_1_national

The referendum fails, but our silence is a vacuum the Right is happy to fill. Hugenberg and Hitler are being hailed as the only "true" nationalists, while the Republic’s defenders seem ashamed of their own policy. The "Liberty Law" didn't pass, but it made the Nazis *salonfähig*—socially acceptable.

@young_2_national
on-arrival: nationalism += 20; socialism += 5; pro_republic -= 5; workers_spd += 2; old_middle_dnvp += 4; rural_dnvp += 5; nsdap_unemployedc += 5; kpd_workers += 7; rural_dvp -= 2; workers_ddp -= 2; workers_csvd += 2; new_middle_kvp += 3

The referendum fails, yet the high turnout for the **"Freedom Law"** has sent a shockwave through the establishment. Even in the "bourgeois" parties, members are whispering that the Penal Clause might have been too far, but the sentiment against "Tribute" is genuine. The National Opposition has found its footing; the "Block of Stone" is beginning to roll.

@collapse
view-if: ((west_relation < 0 and nationalism > 60) or (ruhr_labor = 1 or young_plan_collapse = 1))
on-arrival: west_relation -= 3; nationalism += 5; socialism += 8; workers_spd -= 3; workers_z -= 3; workers_ddp -= 3; workers_dvp -= 3; workers_other -= 3; pacifism -= 1; pro_republic -= 1; labor_dissent -= 10; left_dissent -= 10; reformist_dissent += 10; young_plan_catastrophy = 1; camarilla_strength += 5; hindenburg_patience /= 2; hindenburg_patience -= 15
achievement: ruhrland

Negotiations have shattered. The Young Plan is dead. France, citing German bad faith, has frozen the evacuation and reinforced the Rhineland garrisons. The dream of fiscal autonomy is gone, replaced by the cold reality of bayonets in the Ruhr. Our international standing has evaporated overnight.

[? if president = "Hindenburg": The Old Field Marshal is livid. He views this collapse as a personal failure of the government to provide the stability he was promised. The air in the Reichskanzlei is thick with the scent of an impending dismissal. ?]

@resist
view-if: (reichswehr_strength >= 100 and reichswehr_loyalty > 0.35 and reichswehr_militancy >= 5) and secret_mode and (ruhr_labor = 1 or young_plan_catastrophy = 1)
on-arrival: nationalism += 15; west_relation -= 20; young_plan_catastrophy = 1; pro_republic -= 5; reichswehr_strength *= 0.9; reichswehr_loyalty *= 1.2; italy_relation += 5; soviet_relation += 3; resources += 5; budget += 2; inflation += 1.34; new_middle_spd *= 0.98; old_middle_spd *= 1.07; camarilla_strength += 5; hindenburg_patience -= 10
achievement: reichswehr_ruhrland

The "Miracle of the Ruhr." We have done the unthinkable: met French force with German steel. By refusing re-occupation, we have severed our ties with the West but forged a new, terrifying national unity. The Young Plan is a memory; the future will be written in autarky and blood.

[? if president = "Hindenburg": Hindenburg is shocked by the audacity, but his soldier’s heart is quietly impressed. However, he knows that "stabilizing the situation" now requires a miracle of a different kind. ?]
